            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Gurukul The School is the best choice we made as parents for our son. Our son joined this school in current academic year and since then we could see lot of improvements in terms of his communication skills and day to day activities which he is learning from school. We are specially thankful to Manjusha M’am for being available every time whenever we needed her support and guidance. Her commendable support  extends beyond the classroom. The teaching strategies used and shared with us not just help in quick learning but also makes learning of new concepts interesting for kids. The focus on all over development of kids is also noteworthy. The advanced technologies adopted by the school makes the processes simpler and time-saving for parents. Various amenities offered within the campus for kids are cherry on the top!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
