            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I want to extend my heartfelt appreciation for     the exceptional dedication of the class teacher in nurturing my child's growth. She looks forward to school every day and often talks about how much she enjoys her classes. Your teaching style has not only made learning engaging but has also sparked her curiosity. Your presence as her teacher is truly a blessing.",
          "publisher": {
